  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were four members.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were Judge Biddle, representing the United States, Lord Geoffrey Lawrence, representing Great Britain, Nikachenko, a general representing the Soviets, and Donadeu Vabres, V-A-B-R-E-S, representing the French.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Each of them had a deputy so that if something happened to them, the deputy could fill in without disturbing the progress of the trial.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there were really four main judges and four assistant judges.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, of course, the prosecution had nothing to do with it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But as I understand it from the biography of Judge Biddle and by other reports that we have since the trial, they would normally agree on a consensual basis after discussion on points.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if there was a dissent, what they would do is file a quiet memorandum so that this-- if there was disagreement, let's say three to one, in a vote, it wouldn't-- on a particular point as the trial was going on, it wouldn't necessarily appear on the record.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The tribunal would merely say that the vote of the tribunal-- the decision of the tribunal is such and such.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if there happened to be a dissent, nothing would be said about it at the time, because you can't have a lot of-- of dissents going on during the course of the trial.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think that when they came to the votes on guilt or innocence, there were unanimous votes with respect to all the 19 defendants who were convicted.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] With respect to the three who were acquitted, von Papen, Fritzche, and Schacht, there was a dissent by the Soviet judge.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
